Package: koha-systemd
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, systemd, koha-common
Description: Native systemd service units for Koha ILS
 Provides native systemd service management for Koha instances.
 Each service type (Plack, Zebra, SIP, Z3950, workers, indexers)
 runs as a separate systemd unit with proper isolation, resource
 limits, and monitoring.
 .
 This package addresses issues with the traditional init.d approach:
 - Proper process isolation per service
 - Independent resource limits and restart policies
 - Better observability via journalctl
 - Native systemd integration (MemoryMax, CPUQuota, etc.)
